% [ABSTRACT] — IJCAI-07 core paper: bidding-based protocol for agents with
%              nonlinear interdependent utility functions. Mediator collects
%              bids (sampled utility points) from each agent and finds the
%              combination maximizing social welfare. Formally analyzed.
%              Limit: centralized mediator; static utility functions;
%              full bid disclosure (privacy concern); scales poorly with
